ZH: 我要说服他参加这个计划。
EN: I want to persuade him to join this project.

ZH: 她成功地说服了我买下那辆汽车。
EN: She successfully persuaded me to buy the car.

ZH: 他很有说服力，总能说服别人接受他的观点。
EN: He is very persuasive and can always convince others to accept his point of view.

ZH: 我们需要找到一种说服他们的方法。
EN: We need to find a way to convince them.

ZH: 她用事实和数据来说服了委员会。
EN: She persuaded the committee with facts and data.

ZH: 你能不能说服父母买一只宠物狗？
EN: Can you persuade your parents to buy a pet dog?

ZH: 我们必须说服他们接受我们的提议。
EN: We must persuade them to accept our proposal.

ZH: 他没有说服力，无法改变我的看法。
EN: He lacks persuasiveness and cannot change my opinion.

ZH: 他失败了，没有说服她同意离开。
EN: He failed to persuade her to leave.

ZH: 我尽力说服了他，但他仍然拒绝了。
EN: I tried my best to persuade him, but he still refused.

ZH: 他终于被说服同意了合作。
EN: He was finally persuaded to agree to cooperate.

ZH: 你是否能用事实来说服我？
EN: Can you persuade me with facts?

ZH: 没有什么能说服我放弃我的梦想。
EN: Nothing can persuade me to give up on my dreams.

ZH: 请说服他继续合作。
EN: Please convince him to continue working together.

ZH: 我没有办法说服他改变主意。
EN: I have no way to persuade him to change his mind.

ZH: 我们需要一个好的说服策略来赢得选择权。
EN: We need a good persuasion strategy to win the election.

ZH: 这个演讲者有一种天生的说服力。
EN: This speaker has a natural persuasiveness.

ZH: 他的观点很有说服力，我很容易被说服。
EN: His viewpoint is very persuasive, and I am easily convinced.

ZH: 她用实际行动来说服人们关注环境保护。
EN: She persuades people to care about environmental protection through practical actions.

ZH: 你一定要花点时间来说服他。
EN: You have to take some time to persuade him.
